    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为轮椅侠！</strong>这个游戏抽象但也极具挑战性，纯粹基于物理的运动系统让你体验最真实的轮椅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/2eb9b892ffbaed2b4ef5da303965d594.poster.avif?t=1771746049\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/2eb9b892ffbaed2b4ef5da303965d594.webm?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/2eb9b892ffbaed2b4ef5da303965d594.mp4?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双手控制:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的双手操作系统，挑战你的左右手协调能力！推，拉，手刹，转向，倾斜，克服每一个挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/e49e492edbf98c73ab5750d6e1369248.poster.avif?t=1771746049\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/e49e492edbf98c73ab5750d6e1369248.webm?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/e49e492edbf98c73ab5750d6e1369248.mp4?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逼真的轮椅物理:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于真实的物理，捕捉了轮椅运动的细微之处。你可以选择第三人称或第一人称视角，在轮椅的世界里，即使是最小的坎也可能成为几乎无法跨越的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/9d85b74406bfea807a4bb0a157a1ffdc.poster.avif?t=1771746049\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/9d85b74406bfea807a4bb0a157a1ffdc.webm?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/9d85b74406bfea807a4bb0a157a1ffdc.mp4?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>速度与控制：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索精心设计的赛道关卡，灵感来自使用轮椅的人们日常的生活。在不断磨炼技术的同时发现隐藏路径和道具，使用你的想象力来征服每个赛道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/02835c1bb646b815c86a9c9208df6493.poster.avif?t=1771746049\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/02835c1bb646b815c86a9c9208df6493.webm?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/02835c1bb646b815c86a9c9208df6493.mp4?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>荒诞有趣但发人深思：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将我们看似平凡的事物变成充满欢乐和混乱的挑战，《轮椅模拟器》带给你对行动方式的崭新视角——有趣又暗含深意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/2850faa4b43f9b3819ff7a95a86b99e8.poster.avif?t=1771746049\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/2850faa4b43f9b3819ff7a95a86b99e8.webm?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338350/extras/2850faa4b43f9b3819ff7a95a86b99e8.mp4?t=1771746049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特别声明</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《轮椅模拟器》秉持着对轮椅使用者经历的尊重，旨在为平台游戏带来独特的视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏结合了幽默与富有挑战性的物理玩法，为移动机制提供了新鲜的体验，并鼓励共情与理解。尽管游戏中设置了夸张的障碍和有趣的失败时刻，其目的在于庆祝轮椅使用者面对日常环境时的坚韧和创造力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们希望玩家能在游戏中有所启发，同时收获欢笑。</p>",
